section#step-1.columns.has-text-centered(v-if='wizardStep==1')
    .column.is-full
        a.title(href='https://github.com/nisrulz/app-privacy-policy-generator#app-privacy-policy-generator' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer' aria-label='App Privacy Policy Generator on GitHub')
        img.center-block.hero-image(src='images/app_graphics/side_image.webp' alt='App Privacy Policy Generator hero image' width='2024' height='1132')
        p.is-size-8.mt-2
                | Generate a customized Privacy Policy and Terms of Use document for your apps
        p.mt-2
            | Forever 
            a(href='https://github.com/nisrulz/app-privacy-policy-generator#app-privacy-policy-generator' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer') free and open-source, 
            | built with 
            span.heart ♥️ 
            | by 
            a(href='http://www.nisrulz.com/' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer') Nishant
            |  and 
            a(href='https://github.com/nisrulz/app-privacy-policy-generator/graphs/contributors' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer') contributors.
            br
            a(href='reviews.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer') ⭐️ Check out the Guestbook for reviews 
            span | 
            a.has-info(href="#" rel="noopener noreferrer" @click.prevent="toggleFaqModalVisibility") Read FAQ
        p.mt-2
            a(href='https://bsky.app/intent/compose?text=%F0%9F%93%9D%20App%20Privacy%20Policy%20Generator:%20A%20free%20web-app%20to%20generate%20a%20generic%20privacy%20policy%20for%20your%20Android%2C%20iOS%2C%20KaiOS%2C%20%26%20Web%20apps%0A%F0%9F%91%A8%F0%9F%8F%BB%E2%80%8D%F0%9F%92%BB%20by%20@nisrulz.com%20%0A%0A%E2%9C%85%20Web%20App:%20https://app-privacy-policy-generator.nisrulz.com%20%0A%0A%E2%9C%85%20Reviews:%20https://app-privacy-policy-generator.nisrulz.com/reviews.html%20%0A%0A#free%20#app%20#privacy%20#policy%20#generator' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer')
                img(style='margin-right: 6px' src='https://img.shields.io/badge/Bluesky-0285FF?logo=bluesky&logoColor=fff&label=Share%20on&color=0285FF' alt='Bluesky')
            a(href="#" @click.prevent='toggleDisclaimerModalVisibility' rel='noopener noreferrer')
                img.social-logo(src='images/app_icons/disclaimer.svg' alt='Disclaimer' width='20' height='20')
            a(href='https://github.com/nisrulz/app-privacy-policy-generator' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer')
                img(alt='GitHub stars' src='https://img.shields.io/github/stars/nisrulz/app-privacy-policy-generator?style=social')
            a(href='https://ko-fi.com/nisrulz' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer')
                img(src='images/vendor/kofi1.png' alt='Buy Me a Coffee at ko-fi.com' width='76' height='19' style='border:0')
        hr
        button.button.is-primary.start-btn(@click='nextStep') Start
